{"tid":1535011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報:美若通過香港法案將遭全面報復","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:50:16.000Z","uid":31907,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"89862859bc041b90a3fb635780782b9f25d9090d","tid":1535011,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"環球時報:美若通過香港法案將遭全面報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n放大圖片<br />\n《環球時報》發表社評，點名批評亂港分子黃之鋒、周永康日前投書《紐約時報》，促請美國國會通過《香港人權及民主法》，是主動賣身美國主子，把香港稱作是對抗中國的前線。社評指黃之鋒之流年紀輕輕，屬於漢奸系列的新生代。<br />\n<br />\n社評指，《香港人權與民主法案》是惡意干涉中國內政的霸權法案，一旦通過並實施，中美關係將會受到新的衝擊。而通過現行的《美國&mdash;香港政策法》等，美國給予香港在經貿、金融等方面的優惠待遇決不是什麼恩賜。它固然有利於香港和內地的發展，但同樣也有利於美國，並符合多方利益。<br />\n<br />\n一旦美國取消香港的上述待遇，香港和內地的發展也許會受相關的技術性影響，但包括香港特區在內的中國有能力做出任何應變。中國的命運不會掌握在華盛頓的手中，華盛頓沒有操控中國的餘地。黃之鋒之流鼠目寸光，根本看不懂這個大棋盤。<br />\n<br />\n社評強調，美方的香港這步棋在落子之前可以用來施加威脅，一旦走出，必定是死棋。中國的報復肯定也會是全面的，不僅限於經貿領域。<br />\n<br />\n社評指出，要求美國準備制裁香港，無論出於什麼理由，都首先違背了天理，這種惡行被清算將是必然。又指黃之鋒、周永康們做了一個悲劇性選擇，賣國者在中國歷史上幾乎沒有過好下場，他們的一生最後一定會輸得連底褲都不剩。"},{"pid":"85208445158a4b4f512887ce0b0271e498a5738f","tid":1535011,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2c2db6ee6261e395a36ae33449fe21c73f141c2","tid":1535011,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf1b576f1525b718ef520c5d273c40fc2c26a008","tid":1535011,"uid":249480,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"報啦報啦<br />\n等唔切"},{"pid":"94fb9b6a1294c2b122483798d7db02e5a9f8bb43","tid":1535011,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">楊衛隆：美國嘅香港民主法被泛民拖到十一月才能立法，將會有十萬手足被捕！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513863</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16c43a9fd634de8f2d07a92b00db86c16a6e1183","tid":1535011,"uid":124330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"係就快 攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585fddc5c93b7a332bc0aa24f2eda44b91783c64","tid":1535011,"uid":247184,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"報咩復呀，嚇鬼咩？俾印度佬割撚左塊中國領土add都唔敢add"},{"pid":"f6f5258e3d07d22378959088433ff1caf87b1151","tid":1535011,"uid":16057,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"期待 想睇下你地啲錢係哂外國既情況下點樣報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發窮惡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f584f5e83101fbb82c2ebd1630d069e7ea1cf22f","tid":1535011,"uid":40932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"關你撚事？人地國家事務"},{"pid":"cc25eb699a33d39243dfd9ca6abb98cea51d7ac3","tid":1535011,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"後果自負"},{"pid":"b03616b189bf4680be45292972fe247094af4e1e","tid":1535011,"uid":35429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"快啲報復啦"},{"pid":"8e48c05e64dd9d254ef6f1cdfbf392efd4754635","tid":1535011,"uid":214079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔講條法案有無用 中共好似淆底wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c28043cf9eae5b298ebac4c74ce16febccb8e4","tid":1535011,"uid":161541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiokKv6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiokKv6.gif&h=b05ab9a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d96881e963460b0594dfe0a3524ad882a7147e3d","tid":1535011,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"以「無產階級」革命起家的北京政府，竟然支持林鄭政府打壓香港「工人階級」！"},{"pid":"39e0832b5844a253766c37e4bf1735d2160171d4","tid":1535011,"uid":159216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1PgzbH3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1PgzbH3.gif&h=f862091f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de1578abf3647722348b8dd1ced5ee4d7a6dde91","tid":1535011,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse